Resource Profile: ProfileCapabilityStatement

0.0.1-snapshot-3
Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/5.0/StructureDefinition/profile-CapabilityStatement Version:
Standards status: Trial-use Active as of 2026-02-06 Maturity Level: 0 Computable Name: ProfileCapabilityStatement

This cross-version profile allows R5 CapabilityStatement content to be represented via FHIR R4 CapabilityStatement resources.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Cross-version Extension `R5.ActivityDefinition.participant.typeCanonical` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.ActorDefinition` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.PlanDefinition.action.participant.typeCanonical` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.PlanDefinition.action` for use in FHIR R4... Show 3 more, Cross-version Extension `R5.PlanDefinition.actor` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.RequestOrchestration.action.participant` for use in FHIR R4 and Cross-version Extension `R5.RequestOrchestration.action` for use in FHIR R4

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
